title: Episode 33 - Tristan Thomas Interview (Brink Vault 2012)
itunes:title: Episode 33 - Tristan Thomas Interview (Brink Vault 2012)
description: Another 'vault' episode today as we venture back to 2012 to speak with another Tasmanian Olympic athlete in hurdler Tristan Thomas. Talking up his then recent Olympic experience through to the frustrations he has had through his career with injury, it's a fun chat that we know you will enjoy!
